Name: Reach the Summit
About the game: Reach the Summit is 2D platformer in a pixel retro style. The Brave Leah is an novice climber. She wants to improve herself, and she decided to reach the first hard Summit in her life. Help her to climb up, and get ready to your first adventure with Leah!
